title: [SOLVED]820-3476-A Sensor read problem
message:
Hello Everybody

Working on liquid damaged 820-3476-a . After cleaned SMC area and u1900 around power on but now slow working and fan works high. ASD errors like this,

[B]Sensor Group (test #5) - Limit with Core Load Test[/B]
Verifies a group of sensors defined in SensorGroupLimits.prm.  The test will generate two loads - cpu and gpu - then verify the list of sensors per limits.
[B]ERROR - -13005 [The SMC can not read this sensor] -- TEST FAILED[/B]
Sensor Group (test #6) - Limit with Memory Load Test
- Verifies a group of sensors defined in SensorGroupLimits.prm. The test will generate a memory load then verify the list of sensors per limits.
[B]ERROR - -13005 [The SMC can not read this sensor] -- TEST FAILED[/B]

Also replaced , battery and trackpad with cable but didn't change problem.
note: SMC reballed

title: [SOLVED]820-3476-A Sensor read problem
message: What does U5870 look like? U5870 deals with CPU, Memory, Airflow sensors etc.

title: [SOLVED]820-3476-A Sensor read problem
